docs.title: My Docs
docs.text: Welcome to the documentation for My Docs. This is a simple project to demonstrate MkDocs with the Material theme.

docs.title: Getting Started
docs.text:
To get started, clone the repository and install the dependencies:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/my-docs.git
cd my-docs
pip install -r requirements.txt

docs.title: Contributing
docs.text: We welcome contributions! Please see the CONTRIBUTING.md file for more information.
